Package: addr
Type: Package
Title: Uncertainty Intervals, Quantiles, and Probabilities for Statistical Models
Version: 0.1.0
Author: John Haman
Maintainer: John Haman <jhaman@ida.org>
Description: Functions for automatically appending confidence intervals,
    prediction intervals, and other quantities of interest to data frames. addr
    has a "data frame first" syntax that allows for easy piping. Currently supported models
    include linear and log-linear models, linear mixed models, and generalized linear models.
Depends: 
    tidyverse,
    lme4,
    merTools,
    arm
License: ?
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
